Isang templo ng Zoroastrian?

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:02.060
Kita mo?

00:34:02.160 --> 00:34:04.040
Inaagaw nito ang lahat ng atensyon

00:34:04.070 --> 00:34:05.350
mula sa Earth God Temple.

00:34:05.350 --> 00:34:06.750
Narinig ko na nitong mga nakaraang araw,

00:34:06.750 --> 00:34:08.610
napakasigla doon.

00:34:09.550 --> 00:34:10.150
Bakit hindi ako

00:34:10.510 --> 00:34:12.409
dalhin ka doon para tingnan ito?

00:34:13.360 --> 00:34:14.090
Mukhang maganda.

