Ang reverse psychology na ito kay Fei

00:35:00.710 --> 00:35:01.880
gumagana talaga.

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:03.290
Tara na.

00:35:28.280 --> 00:35:29.630
anong mali?

00:35:30.280 --> 00:35:31.840
Bakit ang lungkot mo?

00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:34.280
Ilang araw nang nawawala ang tatay ko.

00:35:34.590 --> 00:35:36.480
Walang palatandaan sa kanya, patay o buhay.

00:35:36.760 --> 00:35:37.820
Paano ako hindi malulungkot?

00:35:40.230 --> 00:35:41.090
ikaw naman?

