Ngunit tila walang silbi,

00:36:05.230 --> 00:36:06.840
kaya pumunta ako sa Ghost Market

00:36:07.590 --> 00:36:09.450
upang humingi muli ng banal na proteksyon.

00:36:46.360 --> 00:36:48.000
Shi Qiansui.

00:36:48.880 --> 00:36:49.610
sino nandyan?

